text.section:
Each person who rents a motor vehicle, trailer, or semitrailer to another person shall keep a record of:
The registration number of the rented vehicle and, if only a semitrailer or trailer is rented, the registration number of the motor vehicle to be used to tow the trailer or semitrailer;
The name and address of the lessee;
The number of the license to drive of the individual who will drive or tow, as the case may be, the rented vehicle; and
The date and place of issuance of the license to drive.
